<author>Joy F. Patterson</author>
<title>Wannan Rana LW543</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Wannan rana, wannan rana
 Da Allah ya yi, da Allah ya yi
 Mu yi murna, mu yi murna
 Mu ɗaukaka shi, Mu ɗaukaka shi.

[V2]
 Wannan ranan da Allah ya yi (HEY!)
 Mu yi murna, mu ɗaukaka shi (HEY!)
 Wannan rana, wannan rana
 Da Allah ya yi.

[V3]
 2) Wannan sa'a, wannan sa'a
 Da Allah ya yi, da Allah ya yi
 Mu yi murna, mu yi murna
 Mu ɗaukaka shi, Mu ɗaukaka shi.

[V4]
 Wannan sa'a da Allah ya yi (HEY!)
 Mu yi murna, mu ɗaukaka shi (HEY!)
 Wannan sa'a, wannan sa'a
 Da Allah ya yi.</lyrics>
</song>